{"tid":1211334,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[致廣告界] 你不遊行，你也有選擇媒體的自由","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T05:10:41.000Z","uid":13759,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8935adc0682e5905da5c09745265a3f997c0ba60","tid":1211334,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"致廣告界的信📩<br />\n<br />\n小弟都係廣告界人仕，我知道好多香港各大Media Agency都有好多年青人，好多都有出黎反送中。部份公司更罷工反對逃犯修訂條例。<br />\n<br />\n其實你都可以出一分力，同你個客講，為咗維護客戶品牌質素，拒絕同反對佢投放任何廣告Budget（或大幅減少）去所有「是是旦旦」，「不盡不實」，「以偏概全」，同「仆街冚家剷」嘅媒體及KOL。不只限於新聞Section，及旗下所有媒體，包括手機平合及社交平台。<br />\n<br />\n守護客戶品牌，是你作為廣告策略專業人士的責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179ef89e0d9d97717b57a9a0cc2e45caa1799ee0","tid":1211334,"uid":223609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28a655bf2eaaeaac205537f218ae065583402992","tid":1211334,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"各位Agency同In-house Marketing歸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfd3822d4ae2e4af1b3f5642171fc9f206ef5e0","tid":1211334,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5a1a207922bf261a96ee4843bf328b0375b3b5c","tid":1211334,"uid":93131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"126fa269ae4ca871524e9b81d47ad14bbadb542e","tid":1211334,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ccfbc59ba1426f5c1b870c078dea43bd24b4f3","tid":1211334,"uid":12197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b473564bc48932ff5809c8cfb8fb88814001b2f8","tid":1211334,"uid":56743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cite